01:03:47,656 --> 01:03:50,459
<i>♪ I know you want me ♪</i>

1247
01:03:51,861 --> 01:03:55,562
<i>♪ So don't keep sayin'
our hands are tied ♪</i>

1248
01:03:55,564 --> 01:03:58,097
<i>♪ You claim
