1258
01:04:29,665 --> 01:04:31,130
<i>♪ It's up to you ♪</i>

1259
01:04:31,132 --> 01:04:33,167
<i>♪ And it's up to me ♪</i>

1260
01:04:33,169 --> 01:04:36,971
<i>♪ No one can say
