1286
01:06:09,966 --> 01:06:14,134
<i>♪ So just give me all of you ♪</i>

1287
01:06:14,136 --> 01:06:16,303
- <i>♪ It feels impossible ♪</i>
- <i>♪ It's not impossible ♪</i>

1288
01:06:16,305 --> 01:06:18,138
<i>♪ Is it impossible? ♪</i>

1289
01:06:18,140 --> 01:06:22,176
BOTH:
<i>♪ Say that it's possible ♪</i>

1290
01:06:22,178 --> 01:06:25,644
<i>♪ How do we
rewrite the stars? ♪</i>

